dev version after I released KNES v0.1... build breaking changes.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">ps. Do I need any other files than knes.h and knes.lib for compiling with cl65 ?</div>
<br />Yeah only those are needed.</div>

